===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act of [[accumulating]], the state of being [[accumulated]], or that which is [[accumulated]]
#: an '''accumulation''' of earth, of sand, of evils, of wealth, of honors.
# {{legal}} The [[concurrence]] of several titles to the same proof.
# {{accounting}} The continuous growth of [[capital]] by [[retention]] of [[interest]] or [[savings]].
# {{context|investment}} The action of experienced investors buying an asset from inexperienced investors when the price of the asset is low.

